title: Accept Initial LOOTs
body:
DivineDAO has been generously seeded with some LOOTs via its founding members. These LOOTs have already been transferred to the Divine Album. 

This proposal executes a transaction for the Album contract to simply acknowledge these Divine tokens as part of its collection.
author: 0x2de14DB256Db2597fe3c8Eed46eF5b20bA390823
